title: Small LOL YT channels - let's connect and help each other grow.

embed.description: G'day! I'm True North Koala and I make immersive, interactive, and sometimes knowledgeable video content for League of Legends. The goal of my league series ...

body:
Hi all!

My thoughts are simple, as small LOL YT content creators, it can be a difficult road to building our channel. Let's help each other by giving exposure, views, subs and support to through mutual sharing, feedback and traffic.

Post your YT channel here and let's help each other grow.

Cheers
True North Koala

replies.body: "I would very much like to advertise my shitty youtube channel. Others may partake if they wish."
